187
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,300
No...

188
00:12:11,460 --> 00:12:12,700
I'm not mad at you.

189
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:16,520
Then why are you avoiding me?

190
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:20,160
I'm not avoiding you.

191
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:23,880
Techno.

192
00:12:24,780 --> 00:12:27,320
I will do everything for you to forgive me.

193
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,700
I really like you.

194
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:38,080
Let's talk about that later.

195
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:40,920
Type is waiting for me.

196
00:12:44,100 --> 00:12:44,840
I have to go now.

197
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,020
Techno!

198
00:12:55,260 --> 00:12:56,440
My brother...

199
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:58,180
He's so good at running away.

200
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:00,520
He's avoiding you again.

201
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:06,640
I did wrong this time.

202
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:11,100
It's everyone's fault.

203
00:13:12,220 --> 00:13:15,480
I sold my brother for free gifts.

204
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:32,020
Shit!

205
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,880
Why is he so handsome?

206
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:39,160
My damn heart, calm down. I will have a heart attack.

207
00:13:45,900 --> 00:13:47,560
Give me more time, Kla.

208
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:51,940
I never thought of having a boyfriend before.

209
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,900
Shorty, wake up!

210
00:14:23,220 --> 00:14:24,400
What the hell?

211
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:25,840
It's not time for sleeping.

212
00:14:26,380 --> 00:14:27,980
It's so late already.

213
00:14:28,300 --> 00:14:29,660
Usually, you wake up at 5 a.m.

214
00:14:30,020 --> 00:14:31,060
Get up!

215
00:14:32,380 --> 00:14:33,440
Shit!

216
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:34,880
I don't know anything.

217
00:14:35,100 --> 00:14:35,780
I didn't see anything.

218
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:40,460
My two best friends are getting together?

219
00:14:42,680 --> 00:14:43,520
Shorty.

220
00:14:44,060 --> 00:14:45,920
Are you going crazy?

221
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:49,940
I understand if you want to have a boyfriend.

222
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:51,900
But I cannot accept the fact that...

223
00:14:52,340 --> 00:14:54,720
Mai is your wife.

224
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:01,080
Pond!

225
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:02,860
What?

226
00:15:03,180 --> 00:15:04,660
Are you crazy?

227
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:05,840
That's right.

228
00:15:08,020 --> 00:15:09,140
I get it.

229
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:12,360
You have a new buddy now.

230
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:16,640
You already forget about your old friend.

231
00:15:16,760 --> 00:15:17,500
Damn you.

232
00:15:28,140 --> 00:15:29,340
Where are you taking me?

233
00:15:29,580 --> 00:15:30,320
Just come.

234
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:33,960
