235
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:37,160
Stop making a pit bull face.

236
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:38,840
Here it is.

237
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:40,700
You should join this.

238
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:43,380
What is it?

239
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:45,180
A volunteer camp?

240
00:15:45,540 --> 00:15:46,340
That's right.

241
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:49,020
Instead of feeling sad.

242
00:15:49,540 --> 00:15:51,140
You should do something more useful.

243
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:53,360
You should use your time thinking about your boyfriend

244
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:55,360
to do something that you're good at.

245
00:15:55,680 --> 00:15:56,500
Register this.

246
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:59,640
It's better than overthinking.

247
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:27,060
Mai is amazing.

248
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:28,940
He doesn't study here,

249
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:30,860
but he knows about this camp.

250
00:16:33,040 --> 00:16:34,360
It seems like you'll enjoy it though.

251
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:38,640
You told me that you want to go if you have a chance.

252
00:16:40,980 --> 00:16:41,760
Ae.

253
00:16:42,560 --> 00:16:43,400
Ae!

254
00:16:43,780 --> 00:16:45,020
Are you listening?

255
00:16:46,420 --> 00:16:47,540
Can you take a picture for me?

256
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,240
Huh?

257
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:50,440
Since when do you like to take pictures?

258
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:51,140
Just take it.

259
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,020
Fine.

260
00:16:54,900 --> 00:16:56,580
One. Two...

261
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:01,680
