262
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:06,700
This is good enough.

263
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:11,960
Can you tell me what's going on?

264
00:17:15,520 --> 00:17:17,540
You said I don't like to update about my life.

265
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:20,480
I want to try to do it.

266
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,100
It's better than doing nothing.

267
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:26,760
Ae.

268
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:30,080
I'm okay. Thanks.

269
00:17:36,340 --> 00:17:37,140
Are you sure?

270
00:17:37,660 --> 00:17:39,240
