272
00:18:13,260 --> 00:18:16,320
Lucky us that we don't have to carry heavy stuff back home.

273
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:19,540
It's me who carry everything. You didn't help me at all.

274
00:18:21,820 --> 00:18:24,100
Lay, I'm your brother!

275
00:18:27,420 --> 00:18:28,580
What are you laughing at?

276
00:18:31,600 --> 00:18:32,940
I have to thank you anyway.

277
00:18:37,580 --> 00:18:38,660
What about you?

278
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:40,400
What?

279
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:42,680
Did you forget something?

280
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:44,260
Forget what?

281
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:47,720
I came out of the house with just a phone and a wallet.

282
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:49,140
It's probably Lay who forgets it.

283
00:18:50,580 --> 00:18:54,860
He asks you, did you forget to say thank you?

284
00:18:57,260 --> 00:18:59,820
I will tell mom if you still behave like this.

285
